                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi,&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;lustre git tag 2.2.0 fails to build from source:&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;p&gt;cc1: warnings being treated as errors&lt;br/&gt;
mount_lustre.c: In function &apos;set_blockdev_tunables&apos;:&lt;br/&gt;
mount_lustre.c:373: error: &apos;savept&apos; may be used uninitialized in this function&lt;br/&gt;
